      WITH FRAME F-Main IN WINDOW W-Win.
  VIEW FRAME F-Main IN WINDOW W-Win.
  {&OPEN-BROWSERS-IN-QUERY-F-Main}
  VIEW W-Win.
END PROCEDURE.

